## Design notes:
##   - 9 slot types: weapon, helmet, chest, legs, boots, gloves, ring, amulet, crystal
##   - 6 items per slot across rarity tiers:
##       Common (lvl 1):  +5-10 primary stat
##       Common (lvl 10): +10-15 primary stat
##       Uncommon (lvl 15): +15-20, element synergy
##       Rare (lvl 25): +20-30, element + class synergy
##       Epic (lvl 35): +30-40, dual synergy
##       Legendary (lvl 45): +40-55, dual synergy, unique name
##   - element_synergy_multiplier: bonus multiplier when Sprite matches element
##   - class_synergy_multiplier: bonus multiplier when Sprite matches class
##   - equipment_id range: 1001-1999
